channel.title: Old account
channel.description:
Well for a while last year I got bored with my other account(s) so I made this one just to see how good I could make it. I did fairly well. I played for about three months on it. Considering the stats, and the bank, I would say it's fair for what it has stat wise. The only thing I ever botted on it was fishing and duel arena counts. (mostly because I hate fishing lol)
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/zmJPe.png[/img]
this is just purely out of curiosity how much do you think I could get for it? I know the stats aren't that great but it has like dragon boots/whip in bank etc.
